    <br>
    <p style="text-indent: 25px;">To "Utter" is to speak, "Utterless" is to not speak. Depravity is the fucked up part of us all that some try so hard to hide. Utterless Depravity brings out the fucked without a word being uttered. It's a party game that pushes the limits of your humanity. It will highlight the deepest darkest corners of your friends minds.</p>
    <br>
    <p style="text-indent: 25px;">Gameplay is stupid simple! Split your party up into teams, one member draws an "Event" card and has to convey the event to their team without speaking. They can draw or act the event out. They can use props and even other people as props. That's it, just no talking or writing out the words, because that's cheating!</p>
